&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.takealot.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Takealot.com&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, South Africa’s leading online retailer, is looking for a highly talented &lt;strong&gt;Analytics Engineer (Data Platform) &lt;/strong&gt;to join our team.&lt;/p&gt;
