&lt;li&gt;Ability to anticipate, identify, and define problems- seek root causes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attention to detail and accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to collaborate with other members of formal and informal groups in the pursuit of common missions, vision, values, and mutual goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications &amp;amp; Experience:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s Degree or Advanced Diploma in Computer Science, Information Systems, Business Management, and a minimum of 5 years of Business Analysis or related technical experience is required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In the event that a candidate does not have a Bachelor’s Degree

