&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mrd.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Mr D,&lt;/a&gt; a division of the Takealot Group, is looking for a highly talented &lt;strong&gt;Engineering Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to join our team in Cape Town. Please note that this position is a hybrid role.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
