&lt;p&gt;This is a senior position reporting to the &lt;strong&gt;Head of Cross-Border Commerce.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Purpose of the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
